{"id":933480868,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"7Â months","timestamp":1681454786,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"256 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/933480868/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Delete Operation for Two Strings","memory":"10.9 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    \n        int dp[1001][1001];\n    int fxn(string s,string t,int n,int m){\n        for(int i=0;i<n+1;i++){\n            for(int j=0;j<m+1;j++){\n               if(i==0||j==0){\n                   dp[i][j]=0;\n               } else {\n                   if(s[i-1]==t[j-1]){\n                       dp[i][j]=1+dp[i-1][j-1];\n                   }else{\n                       dp[i][j]=max(dp[i-1][j],dp[i][j-1]);\n                   }\n               }\n            }\n        }\n        return dp[n][m];\n    }\n    \n    int minDistance(string s, string t) {\n        return s.length()+t.length()-2*fxn(s,t,s.length(),t.length());\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"delete-operation-for-two-strings","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
